fields.title: 8-Bit Armies
fields.description: 8-Bit Armies is a retro styled RTS game from Petroglyph.

fields.title: Acceleration Of SUGURI 2
fields.description: A shooter based fighting game. Doujin PC title developed by Orange_Juice.

fields.title: Amnesia: The Dark Descent
fields.description: A first-person survival horror game with advanced physics-based puzzles from Frictional Games, the creators of the Penumbra series. Its dynamic of light and darkness and focus on avoidance of enemies rather than combat have been highly influential in recent horror games.

fields.title: Aragami
fields.description: A stealth action game featuring an assassin who has control over shadows.

fields.title: Assassin's Creed Chronicles: China
fields.description: A 2.5D downloadable title for the Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and PC. The game follows Shao Jun, the last remaining Assassin of the Chinese Brotherhood.

fields.title: Batman: Arkham Knight
fields.description: Arkham Knight, developer Rocksteady's return to the Batman series, takes place one year after Arkham City. It promises to expand the open world from the previous game, allowing players to drive the Batmobile through Gotham City's streets.

fields.title: Battlevoid: Harbinger
fields.description: Battlevoid: Harbinger is an epic space adventure RTS developed by Bugbyte Ltd.

fields.title: Bayonetta
fields.description: Bayonetta is a "stylish action game" from PlatinumGames.  The titular character is a witch who can use hair-based magic, as well as firearms attached to her feet, to battle fallen angels and other foes.

fields.title: Bear With Me
fields.description: Bear With Me is an episodic adventure game with a noir inspired theme. It was developed by Exordium Games.

fields.title: Beholder
fields.description: Beholder is a totalitarian themed spying game.

fields.title: Homeworld Remastered Collection
fields.description: A collection of the originals and remakes of Homeworld 1 and 2. Improvements include better textures, models, access to higher resolutions and redone cutscenes.

fields.title: Door Kickers
fields.description: Door Kickers is a top-down real-time SWAT tactics game.

fields.title: Downwell
fields.description: A vertical-scrolling action roguelike that is heavily inspired by Spelunky.

fields.title: TIS-100
fields.description: TIS-100 is a programming puzzle game developed by Zachtronics.

fields.title: Volgarr the Viking
fields.description: A tough-as-nails, retro-styled action game published by Adult Swim.

fields.title: Nuclear Throne
fields.description: A procedurally generated roguelike action game developed by Vlambeer. After creating a prototype called Wasteland Kings for Mojam 2, Vlambeer took the prototype and renamed it Nuclear Throne.

fields.title: Darkest Dungeon
fields.description: A dungeon crawler that seeks to weigh the psychological effects of delving into hellish monster abodes, not just the damage to HP. Team chemistry means more than just skill synergy.

fields.title: Wolfenstein 3D
fields.description: Considered by many to be the progenitor of the first-person shooter genre, Wolfenstein 3D is a 1992 first-person action game that pits the player, as Allied spy William "B.J." Blazkowicz, against the might of Nazi Germany.

fields.title: Tooth and Tail
fields.description: Tooth and Tail is an "Arcade RTS" by Pocketwatch Games, the creators of Monaco: What's yours is Mine.

fields.title: Flinthook
fields.description: Flinthook is a roguelite, grappling hook platformer from Tribute Games.

fields.title: The Stanley Parable
fields.description: The Stanley Parable is an abstract, psychological, dark and humorous meta-narrative that attempts to make its choices void, journey paradoxical and generate discussion about storytelling in video games.

fields.title: Thomas Was Alone
fields.description: An indie minimalist puzzle platformer.

fields.title: Brütal Legend
fields.description: Brütal Legend is a humorous heavy-metal, open-world, action-adventure game with light real-time strategy elements. As Eddie Riggs, lead the people of the Brütal World to rise up against the Tainted Coil demons who rule the world, and their leader, the sinister Emperor Doviculus.

fields.title: Trine 3: The Artifacts of Power
fields.description: Trine 3: Artifacts of Power is the sequel to the sequel to Trine. Partially funded by the EU. This entry will for the first time blend 3D segments with the established 2D gameplay.

fields.title: Metal Gear Solid V: The Phantom Pain
fields.description: The final main entry in the Metal Gear Solid series bridges the events between Metal Gear Solid: Peace Walker and the original Metal Gear, as Big Boss wakes up from a nine-year coma in 1984 to rebuild his mercenary paradise.

fields.title: Psychonauts
fields.description: Developed by Double Fine Productions, Psychonauts is a platforming action-adventure game in which players take on the role of Razputin, a young psychic out to thwart an evil plot to subvert the minds of other powerful psychics.

fields.title: Batman: Arkham City
fields.description: When Gotham City's slums have been transformed into a secluded super-prison, it's up to Batman to uncover its conspiracy in the sequel to 2009's Batman: Arkham Asylum.

fields.title: Hand of Fate
fields.description: A tarot card driven roguelike action role playing game, by Defiant Development from Brisbane, Australia.

fields.title: Metal Gear Rising: Revengeance
fields.description: A fast-paced action game co-developed by PlatinumGames and Kojima Productions. It follows ninja-cyborg Raiden's activities four years after the events of Metal Gear Solid 4: Guns of the Patriots.

fields.title: Grand Theft Auto V
fields.description: Rockstar returns to the fictional state of San Andreas with a crew of three criminal protagonists who work together to pull off high-profile heists.

fields.title: Doom
fields.description: In a world with health regeneration and cover-based systems, one of the longest-running first-person shooter series returns to its brutal, fast-paced roots.

fields.title: Duet
fields.description: Duet is a mobile action game with a soundtrack by Melbourne composer and Gotye multi-instrumentalist, Tim Shiel.

fields.title: Titan Souls
fields.description: Titan Souls is a top down action game where you play as a hero trying to defeat large and powerful monsters.

fields.title: Giana Sisters: Twisted Dreams
fields.description: The third entry in the Super Mario Bros inspired platformer series.

fields.title: Outlast
fields.description: Deep within the abandoned halls of Mount Massive Asylum, amateur journalist Miles Upshur sets out to find a good story, and instead finds an evil presence.

fields.title: The Banner Saga
fields.description: The Sun has stopped in the middle of the sky, the Gods have died and human settlements are being invaded by the Dredge, a race of stone beings. There can be no doubt about it, the world is coming to an end. In this turn-based tactics game, borrowing elements from Norse myth, your clan's continued survival is the only thing that truly matters. Will its banner be stomped into the the ground or fly high and bring back hope to those who have lost it in this desolate cold world?

fields.title: 6180 the moon
fields.description: 6180 the moon is a puzzle-platformer in which players control the Moon as it sets off to find the missing Sun.

fields.title: Luftrausers
fields.description: From the makers of Super Crate Box comes the only game to allow players to create, customize, and fly their own luftrausers.

fields.title: Race the Sun
fields.description: Race the Sun puts players in a solar-powered aircraft that must avoid obstacles at increasing speeds in an attempt to stay airborne as long as possible in a race against the setting sun. Supports the Oculus Rift for PC.

fields.title: Planetbase
fields.description: Planetbase is a strategy game where players guide a group of space settlers trying to establish an outpost on a remote planet.

fields.title: Prison Architect
fields.description: The latest game announced by acclaimed indie developer, Introversion Software, in which players build and manage the day-to-day operations of a maximum security prison.

fields.title: ArmA III
fields.description: Arma 3 is the third core game in the simulation and modern combat Arma franchise developed by Bohemia Interactive.

fields.title: Ashes of the Singularity
fields.description: A new real-time strategy game from Stardock. The player commands on a massive scale with large amounts of units on the screen.

fields.title: Assassin's Creed: Rogue
fields.description: Assassin's Creed: Rogue takes place during the Seven Years' War in and around the American colonies. The protagonist, Shay Patrick Cormac, is an Assassin-turned-Templar who is hunting his former Brothers in the region.

fields.title: Batman: Arkham Origins
fields.description: Two years after beginning his crime-fighting career, Batman faces his toughest challenge ever when the crime lord known as Black Mask hires the eight deadliest assassins in the DC Universe to kill the vigilante who has been interfering in his operations.

fields.title: FTL: Faster Than Light
fields.description: In this roguelike space sim, players are tasked with commanding a customized starship on an important mission through a randomized universe, with vile rebels nipping at their heels.

fields.title: Xenon Valkyrie
fields.description: Xenon Valkyrie is a rogue-like side-scrolling action-adventure game for Windows, Mac, and Linux developed by Diabolical Mind.

fields.title: Kingdom
fields.description: A very minimal strategy game that encourages players to stop and enjoy the scenery.

fields.title: Viscera Cleanup Detail: Shadow Warrior
fields.description: A cleaning simulator by RuneStorm that is set in the Shadow Warrior universe.

fields.title: Galak-Z
fields.description: Galak-Z is a sci-fi roguelike space shooter inspired by anime of the 1970s and '80s.

fields.title: Serious Sam: The First Encounter
fields.description: A first-person shooter where players shoot hordes of relentless monsters while trying to save Earth from Mental and his forces.

fields.title: The Wolf Among Us
fields.description: A prequel to the Fables comic book series, The Wolf Among Us tells a tale of the reformed Big Bad Wolf of childhood folklore (who is the sheriff of a secluded community of fables in 20th century New York City) as he investigates a series of grisly murders.

fields.title: That Dragon, Cancer
fields.description: An adventure game focusing on a true story about raising a son who has terminal cancer.

fields.title: Master of Orion
fields.description: A reboot of the space-faring 4X franchise, Master of Orion. It is being developed by NGD studios and published by World of Tanks' creators, Wargaming.

fields.title: Enter the Gungeon
fields.description: Four unlikely heroes must fight through a fortress inhabited by large sentient bullets (among other gun-related creatures) seeking a legendary weapon in this gun-themed rogue-like "bullet hell" shooter.

fields.title: Furi
fields.description: Furi is an ultra-responsive mix of fast-paced sword fighting and dual-stick shooting. Featuring character designs by Takashi Okazaki, creator of Afro Samurai and a explosive electro soundtrack.

fields.title: Owlboy
fields.description: A 2D platforming action-adventure developed by D-pad Studios for PC.

fields.title: Night in the Woods
fields.description: A story-focused platforming adventure/exploration game with a striking and colorful art style. Taking place in a small town of anthropomorphic animals, the game revolves around college dropout Mae as she tries to get reacquainted with her hometown.

fields.title: Hollow Knight
fields.description: A 2D exploration action adventure game, developed by Team Cherry.

fields.title: Euro Truck Simulator 2
fields.description: Travel across Europe as a trucker delivering cargo in a variety of trucks.

fields.title: Europa Universalis
fields.description: Based on a French board game of the same name, Europa Universalis allows players to take control of a civilization between 1492 and 1792

fields.title: Farming Simulator 17
fields.description: The newest game in the Farming Simulator franchise for consoles and the PC.

fields.title: Final Fantasy XV
fields.description: The fifteenth entry in Square Enix's flagship RPG franchise, set in a world that mixes elements of modern technology with magic, a fantasy based on reality.

fields.title: Hearts of Iron IV
fields.description: The next entry in the series of WWII wargames from Paradox Interactive.

fields.title: Hitman
fields.description: The sixth game in IO Interactive's stealth murder franchise, simply titled Hitman, adopts an episodic design which continually introduces new assassination contracts for players to undertake.

fields.title: Just Cause 3
fields.description: Battle a dictator's forces in a fictional Mediterranean archipelago in this follow-up to the popular series from Avalanche Studios and Square-Enix.

fields.title: Life Is Strange: Before the Storm
fields.description: A prequel to the initial Life is Strange game, focused on Chloe's life.

fields.name: PC
fields.description: The PC (Personal Computer) is a highly configurable and upgradable gaming platform that, among home systems, sports the widest variety of control methods, largest library of games, and cutting edge graphics and sound capabilities.
